 Normans. In the later Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William Daresby was born in 1195, in Warton, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom as the son of William De Daresbury. He married Siegrith in 1221, in Warton, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. He died in 1223, in Lancashire, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 28."},"et":{"1195–1223":"1195–1223","1202–Female":"1202–Surnud","1223–1247":"1223–1247","1150–Male":"1150–Surnud","1247":"1247","1202":"1202","1223":"1223","1221":"1221","1195":"1195","1150":"1150","Warton, Lancashire, England":"Warton, Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Hutton,Warton, Lancashire, England":"Hutton, Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Warton, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Warton, Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1195–1223":"1195–1223","1202–Female":"1202–Kuollut","1223–1247":"1223–1247","1150–Male":"1150–Kuollut","1247":"1247","1202":"1202","1223":"1223","1221":"1221","1195":"1195","1150":"1150","Warton, Lancashire, England":"Warton, Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Hutton,Warton, Lancashire, England":"Hutton, Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Warton, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Warton, Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1195–1223":"1195–1223","1202–Female":"1202–Décédée","1223–1247":"1223–1247","1150–Male":"1150–Décédé","1247":"1247","1202":"1202","1223":"1223","1221":"1221","1195":"1195","1150":"1150","Warton, Lancashire, England":"Warton, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Hutton,Warton, Lancashire, England":"Hutton, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Lancashire, England, United King